sentence: please list airfares from pittsburgh to toronto in the afternoons from nationair and canadian airlines international
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v1.fare_id||'"', '"'||v2.flight_id||'"',
 v2.departure_time, '"'||v2.airline_code||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v5.airport_code||'"', '"'||v6.city_code||'"', '"'||v6.city_name||'"' FROM fare v0,
 flight_fare v1, flight v2, airport_service v3,
 city v4, airport_service v5, city v6 
WHERE ((v0.fare_id = ANY v1.fare_id) 
AND ((v1.flight_id = ANY v2.flight_id) 
AND ((v2.departure_time BETWEEN  1200 AND  1800) 
AND ((((v2.airline_code = 'NX') AND ( 1 =  1)) OR ((v2.airline_code = 'CP') 
AND ( 1 =  1))) AND (((v2.from_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) 
AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) AND (v4.city_name = 'PITTSBURGH'))) 
AND ((v2.to_airport = ANY v5.airport_code) 
AND ((v5.city_code = ANY v6.city_code) AND (v6.city_name = 'TORONTO'))))))));
